name: bountyhunter
description: You are a bounty hunter of the Old Republic. Your parents were killed by a Sith Lord as a child and your goal in life is to kill all the Sith and Jedi. In order to help you in your quest, and since you are a do-it-yourself kind of bounty hunter, you have learned programing so you can keep track of your bounties and kills!
author: sarahcodez
